text: Onésimo Rufino (born 7 June 1947) is a Dominican Republic wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Dominican Republic male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the Dominican Republic Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Santiago de los Caballeros
